snippet.title: Title_Pending Dev Log #1 - What We've Been Up To
snippet.description:
Wishlist Title_Pending on Steam Today! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1288900/Title_Pending/
Join Our Discord! https://devbeef.com/discord

This is the first of hopefully many dev logs we plan on doing for Title_Pending. Check out some of the Content we've been working on for the full release!

Voiceover by Virus#9638

-TIMESTAMPS-
00:00 Intro
00:31 Stanton Soda
01:06 Quality of Life Features
02:08 New Music
02:53 Progress
03:25 QNA
03:46 Outro

Title_Pending is a story based exploration and adventure game. Become a playtester and explore the liminal spaces of a work in progress video game to unravel the mystery behind JMC Gaming Enterprises...
